        {
            "id": 6391946,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 南亞(1303)大跌7.01%，報78.3元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)20日12:12股價下跌5.9元，報78.3元，跌幅7.01%，成交55,656張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)所屬產業為塑膠工業，主要業務為各種塑膠加工品、塑膠原料、電子材料、聚酯纖維之製銷。及染整加工 、配電盤。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲8.65%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.32%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+13,715 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-15,382 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+25,881 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+3,216 張</li> <li>融資增減：+301 張</li> <li>融券增減：-1,123 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
